            "collapsed": false,
            "completed": false,
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "12345678-9abc-def0-1234-56789abcdef0",
                "text": {
                  "ops": [
                    {
                      "insert": "1. Public/Victim Protection Layer — TrackTik is guard-facing only. Zero capability for staff, visitors, or public to self-report, raise SOS, or access guidance. Our QR/NFC system lets ANYONE enter the safety ecosystem in 12 seconds.",
                      "attributes": {}
                    },
                    {
                      "insert": "\n",
                      "attributes": {
                        "paragraph": true
                      }
                    }
                  ]
                },
                "format": {
                  "node": "bullet",
                  "children": null
                },
                "collapsed": false,
                "completed": false,
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "23456789-abcd-ef01-2345-6789abcdef01",
                "text": {
                  "ops": [
                    {
                      "insert": "2. AI Threat Intelligence (ARIA) — TrackTik has ReportPro AI for guard report writing. We have ARIA: real-time risk triage, sentiment analysis on voice reports, threat pattern recognition, predictive heatmaps. Fundamentally different intelligence layer.",
                      "attributes": {}
                    },
                    {
                      "insert": "\n",
                      "attributes": {
                        "paragraph": true
                      }
                    }
                  ]
                },
                "format": {
                  "node": "bullet",
                  "children": null
                },
                "collapsed": false,
                "completed": false,
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "3456789a-bcde-f012-3456-789abcdef012",
                "text": {
                  "ops": [
                    {
                      "insert": "3. Martyn's Law / UK Regulatory Compliance Engine — TrackTik has NO Martyn's Law capability. Zero RIDDOR automation. Our Compliance Engine auto-classifies incidents, monitors deadlines, generates regulator-ready reports.",
                      "attributes": {}
                    },
                    {
                      "insert": "\n",
                      "attributes": {
                        "paragraph": true
                      }
                    }
                  ]
                },
                "format": {
                  "node": "bullet",
                  "children": null
                },
                "collapsed": false,
                "completed": false,
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "456789ab-cdef-0123-4567-89abcdef0123",
                "text": {
                  "ops": [
                    {
                      "insert": "4. Anonymous Reporting / Voice Journal — TrackTik has no anonymous channel. Reports come only from guards. Our Voice Journal lets anyone — staff, visitor, public — report anonymously by voice or text. ARIA flags risk. This is a Martyn's Law differentiator.",
                      "attributes": {}
                    },
                    {
                      "insert": "\n",
                      "attributes": {
                        "paragraph": true
                      }
                    }
                  ]
                },
                "format": {
                  "node": "bullet",
                  "children": null
                },
                "collapsed": false,
                "completed": false,
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "56789abc-def0-1234-5678-9abcdef01234",
                "text": {
                  "ops": [
                    {
                      "insert": "5. Situational Guidance System — TrackTik gives guards post orders. We give the PERSON IN DANGER real-time de-escalation, legal, and immediate action guidance across 8 threat scenarios. No other platform does this.",
                      "attributes": {}
                    },
                    {
                      "insert": "\n",
                      "attributes": {
                        "paragraph": true
                      }
                    }
                  ]
                },
                "format": {
                  "node": "bullet",
                  "children": null
                },
                "collapsed": false,
                "completed": false,
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "6789abcd-ef01-2345-6789-abcdef012345",
                "text": {
                  "ops": [
                    {
                      "insert": "6. Duty of Care Evidence Chain — TrackTik logs guard activity. We log the entire organisational response: who was alerted, when they acknowledged, when they escalated, with SLA countdowns and breach notifications. This is courtroom-ready evidence.",
                      "attributes": {}
                    },
                    {
                      "insert": "\n",
                      "attributes": {
                        "paragraph": true
                      }
                    }
                  ]
                },
                "format": {
                  "node": "bullet",
                  "children": null
                },
                "collapsed": false,
