                "text": {
                  "ops": [
                    {
                      "insert": "SafePass feature (Gold tier): gives VIPs/individuals access to a mobile app to monitor their own patrol. This is the closest thing to our public protection idea — but it's for VIPs who already have the app, not universal zero-friction access.",
