                "text": {
                  "ops": [
                    {
                      "insert": "CRITICAL DISTINCTION: QR-Patrol's QR codes = guard accountability tool (proving guard was at checkpoint). Our QR/NFC = public access portal (giving anyone in danger an entry point into the safety ecosystem). Same technology, fundamentally different purpose.",
